        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "四、简答题"
                    }
                ],
                "level": 1
            },
            "bbox": [
                23,
                23,
                149,
                43
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "1. PMAlign 工具中结果的 Fit Error(拟合误差)、Coverage(范围)、Clutter(杂斑) 的意义"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                23,
                60,
                882,
                83
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "Fit Error(拟合误差)：测量已找到的样板与已训练样板的特征的匹配度(不考虑缺失的特征)，范围为零(完美拟合)至无穷大(拟合很差)。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                21,
                97,
                969,
                156
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "Coverage(范围)：在搜索结果中找到的已训练样板中特征的百分比，范围为 0.0~1.0，仅用于PatMax 算法。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                21,
                171,
                981,
                231
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "Clutter(杂斑)：结果中显示的无关特征数除以已训练模板中的特征数，范围为零至无穷大，仅用于 Patmax 算法。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                21,
                244,
                984,
                304
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "2. Caliper 工具中，使用对比度计分时，X0X1Y0Y1 分别有什么作用，如下图设置，如果某个边缘对比度为 100，他的得分是多少？"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                21,
                357,
                983,
                414
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "content": {
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/fe80043bf5882ad41ca3e662009eb4e29642ce1a21dc2378be10d5657045fed3.jpg"
                },
                "image_caption": [],
                "image_footnote": []
            },
            "bbox": [
                23,
                419,
                438,
                642
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "content": {
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/1e35d24ca442ea8a8ff8d41fede7e2377fa81a81148e570a19f6a52bd722cae2.jpg"
                },
                "image_caption": [],
                "image_footnote": []
            },
            "bbox": [
                436,
                498,
                931,
                645
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "对比度计分时：X0表示最高得分1对应的对比度差值，X1表示最低得分0对应的对比度差值Y0 表示得分为 1，Y1 表示得分为 0。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                23,
                646,
                742,
                681
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "得分计算方式： 对比度值/设定的X0的值 "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "\\cdot"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "得分 除出来的值大于1则按1"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                23,
                683,
                584,
                700
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "Eg：X0 设置为 100，"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                58,
                720,
                211,
                736
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "当对比度差值为 "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "\\cdot"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "时得分为 0.5，"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                95,
                739,
                357,
                755
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "当对比度差值为 "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "\\cdot"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "时得分为0.8，"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                95,
                757,
                357,
                772
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "当对比度差值为 "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "\\pm 2 0"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "时得分为0.2，"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                95,
                775,
                357,
                791
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "当对比度差值为0时得分为0，"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                95,
                795,
                329,
                810
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "当对比度差值为110时得分为1，"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                95,
                813,
                347,
                829
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
